div.span: This diagram illustrates the instance level representation of the process that a student named A who belongs to department of Engineering applies to and wins the Kentucky best engineer award(KBEA). KBEA is based in the engineering excellence program which is self-supporting and approved by the provost. The award is approved by the Dean of Engineering.
